Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.72,0:00:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人家擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島也不肯詳細告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自翻過我衣櫃裏的內衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美…美菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:00:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥大變態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第02話 疾馳的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉迷於眼前的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將到來的毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 人類啊想像下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤機關ARMA部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破第二防線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUDA的援軍還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUDA的MACHINA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「VARDANT 」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國軍第28機動部隊來電
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森次玲二的VARDANT開始與加藤機關戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠藤詩絆 唯絆兩人也正與美軍配合進入戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始大張旗鼓的行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩線同時發動攻勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打算放棄搶奪LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採取新的策略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反了 緒川小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處進行騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我們忙於應付時鑽空子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是打算來搶LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九條美海 山下悟二人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回總部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你們白跑一場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 LINEBARREL方面情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍毫無動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MACHINA不同於一般的ARMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Soil選擇特定搭乘者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回應因子的召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能瞬間移動至因子身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LINEBARREL的因子一定是將機體\N固定於被稱為傳送領域的空間內
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是能進入傳送領域的只有MACHINA吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因子一定就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不是事先情報提示的人選
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LINEBARREL裏本應只有城崎繪美一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑中學三年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在特務情報局正採取監視
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查其背景關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是個完全的門外漢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 今後打算對早瀨怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再觀察下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和LINEBARREL會對這世界帶來怎樣的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱麵包?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 矢島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿浩一沒轍 真來氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我去詳細問他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一點都不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房子修好前儘管住在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎小姐是哥哥的女朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥怎麼可能有女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大變態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要內衣的話用媽媽的也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:07:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是LINEBARREL和我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我不是活得好好的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟也在跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為LINEBARREL的D-Soil修復了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修…復?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懇求LINEBARREL的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「救救他」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你因此而復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為與LINEBARREL共有生命的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我能操縱它和獲得的力量都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 只要與LINEBARREL同在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就擁有常人沒有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉體被破壞也馬上受到修復
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為驅動LINEBARREL的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為「Factor」發揮機能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常人所沒有的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它呢 只要有了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次洗澡上廁所都那麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裏添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和警察說估計也沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過段時間記憶也會恢復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是受災的三浦市美笑町現場報道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有威脅這座城市的敵人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要利用這份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打敗他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在明白這些就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 但今天那樣的戰鬥方式會擴大受災範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本政府似乎打算把一系列事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸結為特別自衛隊新型ARMA的誤啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去想像力的人們的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久嵩 下次也讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記作戰目的 澤渡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是對LINEBARREL的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥數據進行採集 打翻並拖它回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LINEBARREL是特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變世界的最強MACHINA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸納入意料之外的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們手中逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也說明物有所值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總沉迷於尋找樂趣可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經等得夠久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍許找點樂子無傷大雅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真崎 不讓久嵩玩就等於逼他去死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 澤渡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LINEBARREL是實現我們目的所必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「韋馱天」的換裝完成了馬上出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪米特裏和友裏安娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JUDA投入戰場的MACHINA如同預期
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以爭取到作戰行動開始前的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知是佯攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能靠自己戰鬥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦啊 正義的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起的有自己的名字和LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及必須和那些敵人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從哪裏來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天後來怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台ARMA呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的ARMA真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家前面的一棟房子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被ARMA砸個正著 直接夷平了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎 有個白色的傢伙幹掉了那些撒野的ARMA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是特自的新型ARMA吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是隕石的電磁波造成失控
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 昨天掉在神社的森林裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是道明寺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說 被原本保護我們的東西攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說是一樁大麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是失控的ARMA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據政府發表的聲明…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不肯說我的LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 矢島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我保護了這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能被他們歪曲事實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大家知道的話會鬧翻天的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣才有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 現在在這裏召喚LINEBARREL不就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人召不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫LINEBARREL嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台ARMA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是ARMA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是MACHINA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和普通的ARMA完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝了D-Soil 被打中也馬上能回復
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被LINEBARREL選中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我和她能召喚出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的MACHINA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理沙子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在說H的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種感覺真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一和矢島兩個人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種久違的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是被矢島教育而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 早瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降矢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天竟敢放我們鴿子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天別想逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HAMA BAKERY的咖喱麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是10分鐘內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島你也在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就想找機會談談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分鐘內給你們買來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早買好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是究極的跑腿工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微用點力氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼還在干跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為腳程快點就拽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不只是腳程快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島多謝你之前的關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已經不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說降矢他們被人扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是道明寺?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B班一個叫早瀨的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:15:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被當作跑腿的那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那種傢伙為什麼突然發作?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給我看什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天之前軟弱無力的我在這裏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後脫胎換骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為擁有新生力量的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為我把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 不用再有負罪感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別躲躲藏藏的出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤機關ARMA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工業區登陸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量六
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動「HIND-KIND」與「PAIN-KILLER」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫山下和九條
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是昨天的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想再為所欲為了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又有什麼陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢島 下面給你看場好戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義使者的獨角戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟 這樣下去工業區就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座城市的正義由我來維護
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了 兩隻角的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以正義之 名制裁你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼正義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台MACHINA歸加藤機關了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得到LINEBARREL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得見嗎 早瀨浩一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們一起去JUDA吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天主動自報家名的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還扯著嗓門喊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許說我傻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我即是正義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:20:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以外你們這些人 全部是邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的正義會把你們全部搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩一…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡人 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣打下去工業區會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-SoiI復原了機體?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天還是菜烏的毛孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不經過努力就獲得力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太令人不爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些「因子」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是正義的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個就是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鬧夠了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山下 九條
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免有更多損失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道贏不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的正義 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何 最近女孩們主動靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然成為正義的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.83,0:23:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子都看在眼裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於迎來春天?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
